foodSearchCriteria.query: Smoked Turkey Breast for Whole Sandwich
foodSearchCriteria.generalSearchInput: Smoked Turkey Breast for Whole Sandwich

foods.ingredients: HICKORY SMOKED TURKEY BREAST: TURKEY BREAST, WATER, CONTAINS 2% OR LESS MODIFIED CORN STARCH, SUGAR, SALT, POTASSIUM LACTATE, CARRAGEENAN, NATURAL FLAVORS, YEAST EXTRACT, POTASSIUM AND SODIUM PHOSPHATES, SODIUM DIACETATE, SODIUM ERYTHORBATE, SODIUM NITRITE, SODIUM LACTATE. COUNTRY BUN: ENRICHED BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR (BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR, MALTED BARLEY FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), WATER, HIGH FRUCTOSE CORN SYRUP, YEAST, CONTAIN LESS THAN 2% OF CALCIUM SULFATE, SALT, CALCIUM PEROXIDE, MODIFIED CORN STARCH, MALTODEXTRIN, SUNFLOWER OIL, COCONUT OIL, NATURAL FLAVORS, CALCIUM PROPIONATE (PRESERVATIVE), DISTILLED MONO-GLYCERIDES, BHT, CITRIC ACID, SOY FIBER, GUM ARABIC, MODIFIED POTATO STARCH, WHEAT STARCH, ENZYMES [ALPHA-AMYLASE AND XYLANASE], PALM OLEIN, SODIUM CITRATE, PARTIALLY HYDROGENATED SOYBEAN AND COTTONSEED OIL, ACACIA GUM, ASCORBIC ACID, CALCIUM PHOSPHATE, WHEAT GLUTEN. SHARP CHEDDAR CHEESE: PASTEURIZED MILK, CHEESE CULTURES, SALT, ENZYMES AND ANNATTO COLOR. FULLY COOKED APPLEWOOD SMOKED BACON SLICES: BACON (CURED WITH WATER, SALT, SUGAR, SMOKE FLAVORING, SODIUM PHOSPHATE, SODIUM ERYTHORBATE, SODIUM NITRITE).
foods.allHighlightFields: Ingredients: HICKORY SMOKED TURKEY BREAST: TURKEY BREAST, WATER, CONTAINS 2% OR LESS MODIFIED CORN STARCH, SUGAR
